articles.author: Guardian staff reporter
articles.title: Mbappé to return to PSG first-team squad after ‘constructive discussions’ - The Guardian
articles.description: The France captain, who is in a contract dispute with the club, was left out of the squad for Ligue 1 opener against Lorient
articles.content:
Paris Saint-Germain are ready to integrate Kylian Mbappé back into the first-team squad, according to reports.
The France captains future at the club has seemed uncertain following links with a move… [+6392 chars]
